{"name": "odoo-addon-mrp-bom-current-stock", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-mrp-bom-current-stock", "version": "16.0.1.0.0.2", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 16.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/manufacture-reporting", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo-addon-mrp-bom-location", "odoo-addon-report-xlsx", "odoo"], "summary": "Add a report that explodes the bill of materials and show the stock available in the source location.", "upload_time": 1718614366}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fmanufacture--reporting-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/manufacture-reporting\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/manufacture-reporting/tree/16.0/mrp_bom_current_stock\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/manufacture-reporting-16-0/manufacture-reporting-16-0-mrp_bom_current_stock\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/manufacture-reporting&target_branch=16.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# MRP BoM Current Stock\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:05f2c1c89b96b6711c7369e749367178e89aa4f52a7e6f53a9ce8b19dd9e69a6\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis modules extend the Manufacturing App adding a report that explodes the\nbill of materials and show the stock available in the source location.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to *Manufacturing > Reporting > BoM Current Stock Explosion*.\n2. Select Product, BoM and location and click on *Explode*.\n3. Set the proper location (if desired) for all the components displayed if you\n   haven't done so in the related BoMs.\n4. Click *Print Report*.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/manufacture-reporting/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/manufacture-reporting/issues/new?body=module:%20mrp_bom_current_stock%0Aversion:%2016.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ForgeFlow\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Lois Rilo \\<<mailto:lois.rilo@forgeflow.com>>\n- H\u00e9ctor Villarreal \\<<mailto:hector.villarreal@forgeflow.com>>\n- Dhara Solanki \\<<mailto:dhara.solanki@initos.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/manufacture-reporting](https://github.com/OCA/manufacture-reporting/tree/16.0/mrp_bom_current_stock) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.wizard", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2017 ForgeFlow S.L.", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.wizard.bom_route_current_stock", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.wizard..bom_route_current_stock", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.tests", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.tests.test_mrp_bom_current_stock", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.tests..test_mrp_bom_current_stock", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2017 ForgeFlow S.L.", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.reports", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock..reports", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.wizard", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock..wizard", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.__manifest__", "documentation": ["Copyright 2018 Camptocamp SA", "Copyright 2017-20 ForgeFlow S.L. (https://www.forgeflow.com)", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.mrp_bom_current_stock.reports", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": []